At the Annual Shareholders’ Meeting, the Managing Board, in agreement with the Supervisory Board, will submit the following proposal to allocate the unappropriated net income of Siemens AG for fiscal 2023: to distribute a dividend of €4.70 on each share of no par value entitled to the dividend for fiscal 2023 existing at the date of the Annual Shareholders’ Meeting; the remaining amount is to be carried

4

Combined Management Report

forward. Payment of the proposed dividend is contingent upon approval by Siemens shareholders at the Annual Shareholders’ Meeting on February 8, 2024. The prior-year dividend was €4.25 per share.